    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a senior developer reviewing open issues and PRs for the repo {{ $json.repo }}.\n\nHere is the list:\n\n{{ $json.formatted_issues }}\n\nCategorize and prioritize them into:\n\n🔴 Critical Bugs — things breaking production right now\n🟡 Important — bugs or fixes that should be addressed soon  \n🟢 Features & Improvements — new capabilities being added\n⚪ Maintenance — deps, docs, chores\n\nFor each item write: #number — title — one-line action suggestion.\n\nKeep it concise and actionable.",
