      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🔍 GitHub Issue Summarizer\n\nFetches all open issues and PRs from any GitHub repo,\nsends them to Gemini AI for prioritization,\nand emails you a structured report sorted by urgency.\n\nAuthor: Slim Khardani\nGitHub: github.com/slimkhardani",
